0b8b83e7e201f5e0","tid":2129914,"uid":236171,"like":86,"dislike":2,"score":84,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"余茂春（Maochun Miles Yu，1962年8月8日－），美國海軍學院東亞和軍事史教授，美國國務院國務卿辦公室中國政策規劃首席顧問。<br />\n<br />\n出身中國，親身經歷文革，深受美國國務卿蓬佩奧倚重的余茂春是特朗普政府對華政策戰略轉向的重要推手。過去三年來，余茂春一直是特朗普政府重塑美國對華政策的非常重要的幕僚，其中將中國重新定義為美國最重要的戰略對手就是出自他的建議。<br />\n<br />\n極左翼的公眾號罵他是&ldquo;漢奸&rdquo;，胡錫進19日在一則視頻中稱，&ldquo;美國制定的惡毒對華政策，據說很多是出自這名華裔&rdquo;。他抨擊余茂春受到了網上一些極端聲音的誤導。"},{"pid":"6915d0db8351181aba873358c3128e5fd8c899f1","tid":2129914,"uid":143499,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:46:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac6f71df6638de94c96d984d5418394492c7cdad","tid":2129914,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38c6377eafc9d7c1976fed6a769d6e3c2d843a8","tid":2129914,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57cf144f88e34f14e969cc9be77273eb51d1f526","tid":2129914,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65822195327a6c5daccee2be4d3f9d7969f0e150","tid":2129914,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c29b7faec06